OL,3,CMurrell inquiry could help 'restore
OL,4,Cpublic trust' in politics, Labour
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FLabour insists "questions are piling
OL,8,Fup" over former SNP chief executive
OL,9,FPeter Murrell's embezzlement "crime
OL,10,Fspree" as it seeks to force Holyrood
OL,11,Fto hold an inquiry into the scandal.
OL,13,FWith Scottish First Minister John
OL,14,FSwinney repeatedly rebuffing calls for
OL,15,Fan investigation to take place at
OL,16,FHolyrood, Scottish Labour will force a
OL,17,Fvote on the matter this week.
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@CO]qD@^OUrD@FO]
