OL,3,CMurrell inquiry could help 'restore
OL,4,Cpublic trust' in politics, Labour
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FA motion to be debated on Wednesday
OL,8,Finsists that an inquiry is now needed
OL,9,F"to restore public trust in Scottish
OL,10,Fpolitics".
OL,12,FThis could look at the "implications
OL,13,Fand lessons to be learned following
OL,14,Fthe conclusion of Operation
OL,15,FBranchform" ` the Police Scotland
OL,16,Finvestigation into SNP finances, which
OL,17,Fconcluded with Murrell pleading guilty
OL,18,Fto embezzling more than #400,000 over
OL,19,F12 years.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@IO]tD@XOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
