OL,3,CMurrell inquiry could help 'restore
OL,4,Cpublic trust' in politics, Labour
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FMr Swinney has steadfastly insisted no
OL,8,Finquiry is needed at either Holyrood
OL,9,For the House of Commons because there
OL,10,Fhas been a a lengthy police
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FSpeaking last week, the SNP leader
OL,14,Fsaid: "We've had a police
OL,15,Finvestigation, there can be no higher
OL,16,Finvestigation and more forensic
OL,17,Finvestigation than a police
OL,18,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
