OL,3,CMurrell inquiry could help 'restore
OL,4,Cpublic trust' in politics, Labour
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"I therefore do not support the
OL,8,Festablishment of a parliamentary
OL,9,Finquiry, because we have had an
OL,10,Finvestigation and it convicted
OL,11,Fsomebody for embezzling from my
OL,12,Fparty's funds."
OL,14,FHis comments came as concerns arose
OL,15,Fthat the SNP may potentially have
OL,16,Freclaimed VAT on some of Murrell's
OL,17,Ffraudulent purchases ` such as the
OL,18,F#124,000 campervan which was recorded
OL,19,Fas a van on party paperwork.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@OO]
