OL,3,CMurrell inquiry could help 'restore
OL,4,Cpublic trust' in politics, Labour
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FMr Swinney confirmed on Thursday that
OL,8,Fthe party had begun discussions with
OL,9,FHis Majesty's Revenue and Customs
OL,10,Fregarding this.
OL,12,FScottish Labour deputy leader Dame
OL,13,FJackie Baillie said: "Questions are
OL,14,Fpiling up about the circumstances
OL,15,Fsurrounding Peter Murrell's crime
OL,16,Fspree and with public money
OL,17,Fpotentially misused, John Swinney's
OL,18,F'nothing to see here' act is becoming
OL,19,Fincreasingly untenable."
OL,26,@uD@VOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
