OL,3,CMurrell inquiry could help 'restore
OL,4,Cpublic trust' in politics, Labour
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FShe stated: "This is a matter of trust
OL,8,Fand integrity in politics and public
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,F"If John Swinney has nothing to hide,
OL,12,Fhe should welcome the chance to get
OL,13,Fanswers on this sordid affair ` but
OL,14,Ffor some reason he is determined to
OL,15,Ftry and dodge scrutiny.
OL,17,F"The SNP should have led the way
OL,18,Fsetting up this inquiry, but instead
OL,19,Fit falls to Parliament to demand the
OL,20,Ftruth.
OL,26,@oD@MOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
