OL,3,CMurrell inquiry could help 'restore
OL,4,Cpublic trust' in politics, Labour
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"Scotland deserves answers and I hope
OL,8,Fon Wednesday MSPs across the chamber
OL,9,Fwill back transparency over cover-up
OL,10,Fby voting for Scottish Labour's
OL,11,Fmotion."
